ntDown()\\n    }\\n  }\\n\\n  private final case class MessageWithToString(value: String) {\\n    override def toString: String = s\\\"payload:$value\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1778040515672}]}\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1520:     766\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1528:     774\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1542:     788\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1768:     766\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1776:     774\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:1790:     788\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-slf4j_2.13:2.6.21/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-06T04-05-39-561908Z.log:2111:     766\t      case level        => throw new IllegalArgumentException(s\"Unsupported log level [$level]\")\nhuman-intervention-logs/c